{"tid":2302293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鴻海將內地蘋果廠房遷越南","createTime":"2020-11-27T04:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T14:17:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"506c0a229a161f97e8dd04766371703ef04bd862","tid":2302293,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201127/F474T6QI3RHHFEKHQEDBBG2Q7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201127%2FF474T6QI3RHHFEKHQEDBBG2Q7M%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ad334105\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201127%2FF474T6QI3RHHFEKHQEDBBG2Q7M%2F&h=014d1c3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201127/F474T6QI3RHHFEKHQEDBBG2Q7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鴻海將內地蘋果廠房遷越南<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qBA2OON6pYZmWsbjJngDCf8b5mk=/720x410/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2PVD2Z6SVNBPLJWUKRGYMRB4Y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqBA2OON6pYZmWsbjJngDCf8b5mk%3D%2F720x410%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2PVD2Z6SVNBPLJWUKRGYMRB4Y4.jpg&h=cddca191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■負責製造蘋果電子產品的富士康，未來須將部份生產線轉移至越南。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n在中國設有大量工廠的蘋果製造商鴻海開始撤廠。路透社引述消息指，鴻海計劃將部份蘋果電腦及iPad生產線移出中國，搬到越南東北部的北江省。這將是鴻海首次在中國以外生產iPad。消息人士說：「品牌廠要求分散，供應鏈就要動起來，這應該是美國政府的策略。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e230660df1b137ea7dbe6c5546fa1b3f1cced7bd","tid":2302293,"uid":328199,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"近排最大笑話：侵認輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\